<ab facs="#facs_595_r1l32">her hadmar von laber der elter <add><ab facs="#facs_595_line_1592207938742_4335">von geſchiht </ab></add>
                        alſpald hie bey vns </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_596" id="297r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_596_r1l3">Vnd alſo baten vvir cʒeſtund die cʒwen <add><ab facs="#facs_596_r1l2"><expan>Erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Vnd </ab></add>
